#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn2.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga "
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Nandanasutta "
msgstr "14. With Nandana "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn2.14:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho nandano devaputto bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Standing to one side, the god Nandana addressed the Buddha in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.53, sc2
msgctxt "sn2.14:2.1"
msgid "“Pucchāmi taṃ gotama bhūripañña, "
msgstr "“I ask you, Gotama, whose wisdom is vast, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:2.2"
msgid "Anāvaṭaṃ bhagavato ñāṇadassanaṃ; "
msgstr "the Blessed One of unhindered knowledge and vision. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:2.3"
msgid "Kathaṃvidhaṃ sīlavantaṃ vadanti, "
msgstr "What kind of person do they call ethical? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:2.4"
msgid "Kathaṃvidhaṃ paññavantaṃ vadanti; "
msgstr "What kind of person do they call wise? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:2.5"
msgid "Kathaṃvidho dukkhamaticca iriyati, "
msgstr "What kind of person lives on after transcending suffering? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:2.6"
msgid "Kathaṃvidhaṃ devatā pūjayantī”ti. "
msgstr "What kind of person is worshipped by the deities?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn2.14:3.1"
msgid "“Yo sīlavā paññavā bhāvitatto, "
msgstr "“A person who is ethical, wise, self-developed, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:3.2"
msgid "Samāhito jhānarato satīmā; "
msgstr "becomes immersed in samādhi, loving absorption, mindful, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:3.3"
msgid "Sabbassa sokā vigatā pahīnā, "
msgstr "who’s gotten rid of and given up all sorrows, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:3.4"
msgid "Khīṇāsavo antimadehadhārī. "
msgstr "with defilements ended, they bear their final body. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.121, sc4
msgctxt "sn2.14:4.1"
msgid "Tathāvidhaṃ sīlavantaṃ vadanti, "
msgstr "That’s the kind of person they call ethical. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:4.2"
msgid "Tathāvidhaṃ paññavantaṃ vadanti; "
msgstr "That’s the kind of person they call wise. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:4.3"
msgid "Tathāvidho dukkhamaticca iriyati, "
msgstr "That kind of person lives on after transcending suffering. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn2.14:4.4"
msgid "Tathāvidhaṃ devatā pūjayantī”ti. "
msgstr "That kind of person is worshipped by the deities.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
